title: Maren Morris and Ryan Hurd In Studio + Bobby's Mailbag + Eddie Wants To Cut Lunchbox's Hair!
itunes:title: Maren Morris and Ryan Hurd In Studio + Bobby's Mailbag + Eddie Wants To Cut Lunchbox's Hair!
description:
Bobby reads a message from a listener who has a nanny problem...she's been hitting on her husband! Bobby and the crew offer up some sound advice. Eddie thinks Lunchbox looks like a mountain man and wants to cut his hair. Plus, Maren Morris and Ryan Hurd stop by the studio to catch up and perform!
